<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>KahitSan Solutions Corp - Maintenance</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* Background gradient effect */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .maintenance-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .maintenance-card::before {
            content: '‚öôÔ∏è';
            position: absolute;
            top: -30px;
            right: -30px;
            font-size: 6rem;
            opacity: 0.05;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9A961 0%, #E5D4A1 50%, #C9A961 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .maintenance-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: block;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .maintenance-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .maintenance-message {
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .status-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.15), rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08));
            border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #C9A961;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .info-section {
            background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .info-title {
            color: #C9A961;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .info-text {
            color: #ccc;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .contact-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            color: #bbb;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .contact-item::before {
            content: "‚Üí";
            color: #C9A961;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        /* Pulsing animation for the maintenance icon */
        .maintenance-icon {
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% {
                opacity: 0.8;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }
        }

        /* Subtle glow effect */
        .maintenance-card {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.06);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                max-width: 400px;
            }

            .maintenance-card {
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }

            .logo {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .maintenance-title {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .contact-info {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body {
                padding: 15px;
            }

            .maintenance-card {
                padding: 30px 25px;
            }

            .logo {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .maintenance-icon {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .maintenance-title {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            .maintenance-message {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="maintenance-card">
            <h1 class="logo">KahitSan Solutions Corp</h1>
            
            <span class="maintenance-icon">‚öôÔ∏è</span>
            
            <h2 class="maintenance-title">We're Under Maintenance</h2>
            
            <p class="maintenance-message">
                We're currently upgrading our systems to serve you better. 
                Our space will be back online shortly with improved features and performance.
            </p>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <h3 class="info-title">
                    üìû Need Immediate Assistance?
                </h3>
                <p class="info-text">
                    If you have an urgent booking or inquiry, please reach out to us directly.
                </p>
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <div class="contact-item">Contact us on Facebook</div>
                    <div class="contact-item">Visit us on-site</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-note">
                Thank you for your patience while we improve your coworking experience.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>